  <testcase name="document_converter_selection_algorithm" classname="com.techleadguru.phase3.day45.Day45MessageConverterTest" time="0.004">
    <system-out><![CDATA[[DAY 45] HTTP MESSAGE CONVERTER SELECTION:

  On WRITE (response body):
    1. Get desired media types from Accept header
    2. For each converter: canWrite(returnType, mediaType)?
    3. Find best match (highest quality factor q=)
    4. If no match → 406 Not Acceptable

  On READ (request body):
    1. Get Content-Type from request header
    2. For each converter: canRead(paramType, contentType)?
    3. First matching converter wins
    4. If no match → 415 Unsupported Media Type

  REGISTRATION:
    extendMessageConverters()  → ADDS (keep Jackson)
    configureMessageConverters() → REPLACES (removes Jackson!)
]]></system-out>
  </testcase>
